file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Whitelist - Request body processing
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /foo:
    post:
      summary: Add foo entity
      requestBody:
        description: Foo item to add
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/FooPayload'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Foo item created

components:
  schemas:
    FooPayload:
      type: object
      properties:
        label:
          type: string
